{"tid":954461,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"人生冇22了","createTime":"2018-12-24T15:15:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-06T14:56:24.000Z","uid":168930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"18bc930afe04bbc5e068cb8c9c2eac58d7587fbd","tid":954461,"uid":168930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T15:15:16.000Z","msg":"日日都輸緊錢 唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n生活又過得唔好...<br />\n我決定每日放負...<br />\n記錄低人生點解冇22<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"712f8b035926168cdefe3b35128aecf15625ff3c","tid":954461,"uid":168930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T15:16:51.000Z","msg":"2018 12 24<br />\n今日個市又繼續跌<br />\n喺broker啲錢又繼續跌<br />\n睇埋美股仲係幾百幾百咁跌<br />\n都唔知幾時先跌完<br />\n人生冇22了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b33c52a08b8f051de613e8c2611eb6eaf0178e98","tid":954461,"uid":168930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T14:55:26.000Z","msg":"2018 12 25<br />\n今日明明係聖誕節<br />\n喺街上面見到個個都一對對咁<br />\n自己淨係可以返聖企打機<br />\n會唔會淨低嘅人生都係咁過<br />\n人生冇22了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65981982924856d26a8cb859a4dda9ceb6d00e48","tid":954461,"uid":168930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T15:26:36.000Z","msg":"2018 12 26<br />\n點解個天要咁對我....<br />\n屋企錢又冇<br />\n家庭溫暖又冇<br />\n連畀個好好睇睇嘅外觀我去探索世界都唔得<br />\n點解要將所有差嘅野放哂喺我身上<br />\n我都係想好似個正常人咁識下朋友出吓街姐<br />\n唉 有時生存都唔知有咩用<br />\n人生無22了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f27d65ad1d7c5271215a494409e4bc678351d2da","tid":954461,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T15:31:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cd6e5e96a9520fedf9306d8efb87c7b9b87be99","tid":954461,"uid":168930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T15:31:04.000Z","msg":"2018 12 27<br />\n原本隻股照早都升緊<br />\n但下午倒跌返<br />\n覺得自己好冇用<br />\n根本就唔識玩<br />\n臨收市前入咗熊<br />\n希望聽日會升<br />\n成日輸<br />\n人生冇22了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdd213ddb44c598df9b9d1a3716381140b4b7a7d","tid":954461,"uid":168930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T12:53:05.000Z","msg":"2018 12 28<br />\n買完熊證夜期又即刻彈........<br />\n算啦唉 我都係唔啱玩股票<br />\n星期一開市all in牛證算數....<br />\n輸哂佢就輸哂佢啦 <br />\n反正有錢都冇人同我一齊享受<br />\n人生冇22了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db6a2b19c955c89bebda3af71d2f76e0f8487703","tid":954461,"uid":52448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T17:29:51.000Z","msg":"巴打擺哂成副身家係股票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?<br />\n輸哂後諗住點?"},{"pid":"a23cef91eade863bb7abc6890e16e86dd085d51e","tid":954461,"uid":168930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T15:58:27.000Z","msg":"2018 12 29<br />\n今日去買m記<br />\n原來嗌咗個豬柳蛋<br />\n但係最後畀咗個香雞包我<br />\n毒撚性格又唔夠膽叫佢幫我換返<br />\n唉...<br />\n人生冇22了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2205365aede966c388e672d5274115cde646ac1","tid":954461,"uid":168930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T12:20:40.000Z","msg":"2019 01 02 <br />\n屌。。。。今日跌果700幾點夾爆哂我啲牛。。。。<br />\n人地仲諗住之前跌咁多<br />\n彈下都得掛。。。。。<br />\n點知。。。。。<br />\n唔緊要。。。。聽日借錢再all in多次牛<br />\n嘿嘿......<br />\n人生冇22了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b67fe46e892e7c8a3ae8b8ae87b1b3d99753190","tid":954461,"uid":35105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T12:37:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74f830807dd47414c4965eea65d05973acf10020","tid":954461,"uid":165024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b67fe46e892e7c8a3ae8b8ae87b1b3d99753190","tid":954461,"uid":35105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T12:37:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T12:39:48.000Z","msg":"funson <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"221390e189bec928e008c96804258c28dbbbc2cd","tid":954461,"uid":35105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74f830807dd47414c4965eea65d05973acf10020","tid":954461,"uid":165024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b67fe46e892e7c8a3ae8b8ae87b1b3d99753190","tid":954461,"uid":35105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T12:37:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T12:39:48.000Z","msg":"funson <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T12:42:19.000Z","msg":"下？？？？？"},{"pid":"c40696654e158948820d9bb09e2a3d8a97974186","tid":954461,"uid":168930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T13:51:55.000Z","msg":"2019 01 03 1<br />\n今日出街果陣唔記得帶傘<br />\n淋到濕哂都冇人遮我<br />\n曾經有一刻有個靚女姐姐同我四目交投<br />\n但係下一秒即刻避開我嘅眼神<br />\n唉 其實毒撚都想有愛<br />\n人生冇22了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"286e54cac128a455af7b47b0018f0d7d7287e090","tid":954461,"uid":168930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T15:39:17.000Z","msg":"2018 01 04 0<br />\n夾爆哂啲牛先黎大爆升<br />\n大户你係得既<br />\n輸咗既錢就如流水般永不復反<br />\n即使掏盡浮生之力去抓緊<br />\n也無法獨臂抗衡那洪濤的激流<br />\n要離開<br />\n但那磅礡的溪流不絕地挑釁着身體每一隅的細胞<br />\n勾起那段熟悉的記憶操作，身體無聲地附和<br />\n教人欲拒還迎，無法斷絕<br />\n也許從甫踏進股市的一刻<br />\n我就知道<br />\n哪怕於一片氤氳中探石而行，有着下一秒隨時喪命的危機<br />\n也要覓得那藏於夢中的禁果，好解心中那縱橫世俗的慾望<br />\n無法斷絕<br />\n無法斷絕那令人沸騰的回憶<br />\n我再也回不去了<br />\n人生冇22了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82beea10dc25079d04ede05bbe64908021ce4862","tid":954461,"uid":168930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T13:27:23.000Z","msg":"2018 01 05 1<br />\n上網訓教上網訓教<br />\n人生冇22了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fca54b05630b0636d93e980806a4963c06de12b","tid":954461,"uid":168930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T14:20:22.000Z","msg":"2018 01 06 0<br />\n今天幫媽媽掃地<br />\n她犒賞了我一粒糖<br />\n人生有22了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b38a5e56590d2427829ed7b30b9f93050fcee531","tid":954461,"uid":8500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T14:56:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}